  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support regulatory submissions and pre-market evaluation of spinal implant constructs; the ensemble predictions have informed device design decisions across multiple product families.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-cbending",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-ensemble-pedicle-screw",
